{"tid":2374022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球逾9600萬人確診　荷蘭擬宵禁及停飛英國等航班","createTime":"2021-01-21T02:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T02:20:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e54cad795403c7e6d79cded77d7ad0bcdf38e5","tid":2374022,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:20:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571504-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571504-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=04d0220c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571504-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e7c0574c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571504-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國約翰霍普金斯大學數字顯示，全球累計有超過9600萬宗新型肺炎確診個案，超過200萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n英國再多1820人死於新型肺炎，連續第二日創疫情爆發以來的單日新高。荷蘭當地星期五傍晚開始在全國範圍實施宵禁令，並停飛往返英國、南非和多個南美國家的航班。"}]}